{"url":"https://www.ags.co.jp/saiyou/interview/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n\n<head>\n  <!-- Google Tag Manager -->\n<script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':\nnew Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],\nj=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=\n'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);\n})(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-TTNJQPHG');</script>\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager -->\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\">\n  <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n\n  <title>社員インタビュー｜ITを変革するＡＧＳ｜採用サイト</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"ＡＧＳの先輩社員のインタビューをご紹介します。ＡＧＳを選んだ理由や働き方、これから入社される方へのメッセージをご覧ください。\">\n  <!-- canonical -->\n  <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.ags.co.jp/saiyou/interview/index.html\" />\n  <!-- OGP -->\n  <meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"ja_JP\" />\n  <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\">\n  <meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"採用情報 | ＡＧＳ株式会社\">\n  <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"社員インタビュー｜ITを変革するＡＧＳ｜採用サイト\">\n  <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"ＡＧＳの先輩社員のインタビューをご紹介します。ＡＧＳを選んだ理由や働き方、これから入社される方へのメッセージをご覧ください。\">\n  <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.ags.co.jp/saiyou/interview/\">\n  <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.ags.co.jp/saiyou/assets/img/common/ogp.png\">\n  <!-- Twitter共通設定 -->\n  <meta name=\"twitter:site\" content=\"採用情報 | ＡＧＳ株式会社\">\n  <meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" />\n  <meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"社員インタビュー｜ITを変革するＡＧＳ｜採用サイト\" />\n  <meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"ＡＧＳの先輩社員のインタビューをご紹介します。ＡＧＳを選んだ理由や働き方、これから入社される方へのメッセージをご覧ください。\" />\n  <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.ags.co.jp/saiyou/assets/img/common/ogp.png\" />\n\n\n\n  <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.ags.co.jp/favicon.ico\">\n\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&family=Jost:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@500&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <link href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/yakuhanjp@3.4.1/dist/css/yakuhanjp.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/saiyou/assets/css/main.css?v=260415\">\n</head>\n\n<body class=\"is-top\">\n  <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n<noscript><iframe src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-TTNJQPHG\"\nheight=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"display:none;visibility:hidden\"></iframe></noscript>\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n  <div class=\"layout-container\">\n    <header class=\"layout-header\">\n      <div class=\"layout-header__inner\">\n        <div class=\"header-logo\">\n          <a href=\"/saiyou/\">\n            <span class=\"header-logo__image\">\n              <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/common/logo.png\" alt=\"AGS CORPORATION\" width=\"150\" height=\"51\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"header-logo__text\">新卒・キャリア<br class=\"only-pc\">採用サイト</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"header-button only-sp\">\n          <button class=\"js-click\" data-click=\"hamburger\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"layout-header__content\">\n          <nav class=\"header-nav\">\n            <div class=\"header-nav__inner\">\n              <ul class=\"header-list hover-color\">\n                <li class=\"header-list__item\">\n                  <a href=\"/saiyou/numbers/\">数字で見るＡＧＳ</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"header-list__item\">\n                  <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/\">社員インタビュー</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"header-list__item\">\n                  <a href=\"/saiyou/hr-message/\">採用責任者メッセージ</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"header-list__item\">\n                  <a href=\"/saiyou/r-message/\">採用担当者メッセージ</a>\n                </li>\n\t\t\t\t  <li class=\"header-list__item only-sp\">\n                  <a href=\"https://www.ags.co.jp/corporate/outline/index.html\">会社情報</a>\n                </li>\n\t\t\t\t  <li class=\"header-list__item only-sp\">\n                  <a href=\"https://ags.smktg.jp/public/application/add/123\">お問い合わせ</a>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n              <ul class=\"header-buttons hover-outline\">\n                <li class=\"header-buttons__item\">\n                  <a href=\"/saiyou/new/\">\n                    <span>新卒採用</span>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"header-buttons__item\">\n                  <a href=\"/saiyou/career/\">\n                    <span>キャリア採用</span>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n    <main class=\"layout-content\">\n<section class=\"section component-header\">\n  <div class=\"component-background\">\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 2423 1518\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid slice\">\n    <defs>\n      <linearGradient id=\"gradient-stroke\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0%\">\n        <stop offset=\"32%\" stop-color=\"#d3edf8\"></stop>\n        <stop offset=\"44%\" stop-color=\"#cef4f2\"></stop>\n        <stop offset=\"63%\" stop-color=\"#ffe7db\"></stop>\n      </linearGradient>\n    </defs>\n    <path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"url(#gradient-stroke)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" d=\"M90.1000,385.001 C91.155,384.965 332.130,688.488 815.610,765.887 C1099.052,809.556 1468.456,754.845 1637.1000,622.1000 C1760.645,516.109 1806.136,452.090 1815.999,310.1000 C1808.923,213.713 1772.364,132.526 1685.1000,99.000 C1629.544,78.449 1548.514,95.358 1483.005,142.196 C1386.240,211.382 1295.211,366.536 1348.1000,574.1000 C1432.369,898.114 1813.031,1243.009 2287.1000,1383.000\"></path>\n  </svg>\n</div>\n\n  <div class=\"section__inner\">\n    <nav class=\"component-breadcrumb\">\n      <ul class=\"component-breadcrumb-list hover-color\">\n        <li class=\"component-breadcrumb-list__item\">\n          <a href=\"/saiyou/\">トップ</a>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"component-breadcrumb-list__item\">社員インタビュー</li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n    <h1 class=\"component-header__heading\">\n      <span class=\"component-header__heading-en\">INTERVIEW</span>\n      <span class=\"component-header__heading-ja\">社員インタビュー</span>\n    </h1>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section component-anchor\">\n  <div class=\"component-button component-button--self\">\n    <a href=\"#interview\">インタビュー</a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"component-button component-button--self\">\n    <a href=\"#videomsg\">ビデオメッセージ</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section interview-sort\">\n  <div class=\"section__inner\">\n    <ul class=\"interview-sorts hover-button\">\n      <li class=\"interview-sorts__item\">\n        <p class=\"interview-sorts__label\">新卒・キャリア</p>\n        <ul class=\"interview-sorts-list\">\n          <li class=\"interview-sorts-list__item\">\n            <button class=\"js-sort\" type=\"button\" data-join=\"new\">新卒</button>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"interview-sorts-list__item\">\n            <button class=\"js-sort\" type=\"button\" data-join=\"career\">キャリア</button>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"interview-sorts__item\">\n        <p class=\"interview-sorts__label\">職種</p>\n        <ul class=\"interview-sorts-list\">\n          <li class=\"interview-sorts-list__item\">\n            <button class=\"js-sort\" type=\"button\" data-type=\"ie\">インフラエンジニア</button>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"interview-sorts-list__item\">\n            <button class=\"js-sort\" type=\"button\" data-type=\"se\">システムエンジニア</button>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"interview-sorts-list__item\">\n            <button class=\"js-sort\" type=\"button\" data-type=\"sales\">営業</button>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p class=\"interview-sort__button hover-button\">\n      <button class=\"js-sort\" type=\"button\">選択を解除</button>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section interview-index\" id=\"interview\">\n  <div class=\"section__inner\">\n    <ul class=\"component-interview component-interview--sort hover-color js-inview fadein-up\">\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"new\" data-type=\"ie\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail15/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview15_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview15_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>インフラエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">特殊な環境でのインフラ構築。試行錯誤の先に見えた、壁を突破する確かな手ごたえ</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2024年 新卒入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"new\" data-type=\"se\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail13/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview13_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview13_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>システムエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">IT未経験から“銀行為替システム”の最前線へ──学びの環境で下流から上流に挑む成長ストーリー</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2020年 新卒入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"new\" data-type=\"se\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail11/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview11_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview11_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>システムエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">地元埼玉で“給与×IT”を極める　自社データセンターで支える若手エンジニアの成長譚</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2023年 新卒入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"new\" data-type=\"se\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail12/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview12_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview12_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>システムエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">職場見学が決め手！仲間と支える公共システム保守エンジニアのリアルな一日</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2024年 新卒入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"new\" data-type=\"sales\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail10/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview10_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview10_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>営業</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">“自分らしさ”を引き出す面接から始まった──風通し抜群のＡＧＳで挑む法人営業の第一歩</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2023年 新卒入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"new\" data-type=\"sales\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail14/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview14_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview14_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>営業</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">体育会仕込みの“忍耐×チーム力”で挑む自治体DX──人柄に惹かれた若手営業の成長ストーリー</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2022年 新卒入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"ie\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail01/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview01_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview01_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>インフラエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">前職の金融業務知識を活かしつつ、未経験でもインフラエンジニアとしてキャリアアップできる</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2024年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"ie\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail04/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview04_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview04_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>インフラエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">地元で腰を据えながら、技術とマネジメントの両面で成長を実感しています</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2022年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"se\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail03/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview03_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview03_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>システムエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">以前と比べ、より高度なスキルが求められるプロジェクトに携わることで大変さの中に大きなやりがいを実感</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2025年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"se\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail02/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview02_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview02_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>システムエンジニア</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">風通しの良さが成長を加速　経験を即戦力に変える、公共医療システム運用の舞台</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2023年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"sales\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail06/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview06_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview06_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>営業</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">IT業界は“ほぼ異業種への挑戦”「これまで知らなかった世界に触れられる」ことにワクワクしています</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2025年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"sales\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail09/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview09_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview09_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>営業</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">「持続可能な未来への貢献」というＡＧＳのミッションに共感し「瞬間的な成功ではなく中長期的視点で考え行動する」営業を目指しています</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2024年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"sales\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail08/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview08_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview08_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>営業</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">ＡＧＳでは困っていることがあれば年齢や役職に関係なくサポートする文化があり「働くヒトそのもの」が最大の強み</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2024年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n      <li class=\"component-interview__item js-sort-item\" data-join=\"career\" data-type=\"sales\">\n        <a href=\"/saiyou/interview/detail05/\">\n          <figure class=\"component-interview__image\">\n            <picture>\n              \n                <source srcset=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview05_thum.png\" media=\"(max-width: 768px)\">\n                <img src=\"/saiyou/assets/img/interview05_thum.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" width=\"380\" height=\"460\">\n              \n            </picture>\n            <figcaption>営業</figcaption>\n          </figure>\n          <div class=\"component-interview__content\">\n            <h3 class=\"component-interview__heading hover-color__text\">変化の激しい時代に「常に変革を続ける」ＡＧＳの一員として顧客と社会の双方に価値を創出</h3>\n            <p class=\"component-interview__text hover-color__text\">\n              2022年 キャリア入社\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </li>\n      \n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"section interview-index\" id=\"videomsg\">\n  <div class=\"section__inner\">\n    <div class=\"interview-index-video\">\n      <h2 class=\"section__heading\">ビデオメッセージ</h2>\n      <ul class=\"interview-index-videos js-inview fadein-up\">\n\n        <li class=\"interview-index-videos__item\">\n          <div class=\"interview-index-videos__movie\">\n            <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rxi-Jcj0uxE?si=d8ETBZ2rokN3ApMU\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n\n\n\n        <li class=\"interview-index-videos__item\">\n          <div class=\"interview-index-videos__movie\">\n            <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WusE9Tlc0sw?si=ds2j8DHkosI3RHDA\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\n          </div>\n        </li>\n\n\n\n        <li class=\"interview-index-videos__item\">\n          <div class=\"interview-index-videos__movie\">\n            <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aSKw_24vIT8?si=LInsslNUYSp-yX7l\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\n  